# ✅ All API keys are production-ready (not test/sandbox)
# ✅ SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL uses your verified domain
# ✅ AWS S3 bucket has proper CORS and permissions
# ✅ Environment variables are set in your hosting platform
# 
# Security Notes:
# - Never commit .env files to version control
# - Use strong, unique passwords for all services
# - Enable 2FA on all external service accounts
# - Regularly rotate API keys and secrets